      "instruction": "<p>Take your <strong>chicken </strong>out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air, then boil a kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>linguine</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 8-10 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once cooked, drain the <strong>cooked</strong> <strong>linguine</strong> and set aside until later</p>",
