      "instruction": "<p>Reduce the heat to medium-high and add your<strong> Chinese rice wine</strong> to the pan to cook for 30 secs, then pour in the <strong>tomato stock</strong></p><p>Cook for 6-8 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) and the sauce has reduced to a pasta sauce-like consistency</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> and remove from the heat</p>",
